{
  "stem": "13690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he came home, we had to confess to the man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We cannot just simply say nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We told him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, 'Look, I'm very upset about it, but I have to think something about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have to do some really thinking.' He liked very much my brother, and he spoke to my brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they came back after discussion that the best thing will be to, at night, at the late hour, meaning not, say, before midnight, that we should go out to that group of houses in the village, of the group of village that we are, and scare off a little bit the people.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Meaning 'we,' he meant to say the following.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew Eli, my brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He looked like a Gentile in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had blonde hair, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had another uncle had also very light complexion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, and he organized, that my brother, two of my uncles, and myself is four.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He himself is five.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One man was sick-- he couldn't go, so we were five.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, 'We have to go five of us and showing that we are some type of partisans, or pretending that we are partisans, and to scare off the people in that group of houses.' Scaring off, not by, God forbid, of doing something bad to them, just scaring them off.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There should be no denunciation of any thinking and any collaborations with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a crazy idea, we really thought.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it turned out to be it was a very wise idea.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The man, which I have to say was illiterate, but was highly intelligent, if he could have thought of-- of hiding, and helping, and feed 10 Jews.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
